OL,3,CThree charged for multi-million pound
OL,4,Cfraud at prestigious sixth form
OL,6,FThree people have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with a multi-million-pound
OL,8,Ffraud at a leading sixth form in Wales.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police have charged two
OL,11,Fmen and a woman in connection with
OL,12,Fsuspected financial irregularities at
OL,13,FCardiff Sixth Form College between
OL,14,F2012 and 2016.
OL,16,FYasmin Anjum Sarwar, 43, from Cyncoed,
OL,17,FCardiff and Nadeem Sarwar, 48, from
OL,18,FPentwyn, Cardiff have been charged
OL,19,Fwith multiple theft and fraud offences
OL,20,Fworth around #5 million.
