OL,3,CThree charged for multi-million pound
OL,4,Cfraud at prestigious sixth form
OL,6,FRagu Sivapalan, 39, from Penylan,
OL,7,FCardiff has been charged with false
OL,8,Faccounting between 2013 and 2016.
OL,10,FAll three are due to appear before
OL,11,FCardiff Magistrates Court on Tuesday
OL,12,FApril 8.
OL,14,FThe college, a fee-paying school for
OL,15,F16- to 18-year-olds, regularly records
OL,16,Fsome of the highest A-level results in
OL,17,Fthe country.
OL,19,FIn 2016 it was the subject of the BBC
OL,20,Fdocumentary Britain's Brainiest School.
